<section class="fz-why-us">
  <div class="container fz-why-us__inner">

    <div class="fz-why-us__left">
      <p class="fz-why-us__eyebrow">The FlyntraZone Promise</p>
      <h2 class="fz-why-us__title">Crafted for the Bold. Built to Last.</h2>
      <p class="fz-why-us__body">We're not just a clothing brand — we're a movement. FlyntraZone was born from a passion for streetwear that doesn't compromise on quality. Every piece is crafted using premium fabrics, thoughtful cuts, and attention to detail that you can feel the moment you wear it.</p>
      <a href="/collections" class="fz-why-us__cta">Explore the Collection →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="fz-why-us__right">

      <div class="fz-why-us__feature">
        <div class="fz-why-us__icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Premium Fabric Only</h4>
          <p>We source only 220–280 GSM cotton for every piece. No compromise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fz-why-us__feature">
        <div class="fz-why-us__icon" style="background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); color: #a78bfa;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ships in 24 Hours</h4>
          <p>We process & dispatch every order within 24 hours of placement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fz-why-us__feature">
        <div class="fz-why-us__icon" style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); color: #34d399;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Wash-Proof Prints</h4>
          <p>Our DTF & discharge prints stay vibrant through 100+ washes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fz-why-us__feature">
        <div class="fz-why-us__icon" style="background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12); color: #f87171;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Made with Love</h4>
          <p>Every stitch is a statement. We pour passion into every collection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.fz-why-us {
  padding: 80px 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #f0f0ff 100%);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
}

.fz-why-us__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
}

.fz-why-us__eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #7c3aed;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
}

.fz-why-us__title {
  font-family: "Bebas Neue", "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: #1a0533;
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}

.fz-why-us__body {
  color: #4b4b6a;
  font-size: 0.97rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin: 0 0 28px;
}

.fz-why-us__cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #7c3aed;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #7c3aed;
  padding-bottom: 2px;
  transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.fz-why-us__cta:hover {
  color: #5b21b6;
  border-color: #5b21b6;
}

.fz-why-us__right {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
}

.fz-why-us__feature {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 18px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  background: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
}

.fz-why-us__feature:hover {
  transform: translateX(6px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12);
  border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
}

.fz-why-us__icon {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 46px;
  height: 46px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12);
  color: #f59e0b;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.fz-why-us__feature h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-body, "Inter", sans-serif);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a0533;
  margin: 0 0 4px;
  text-transform: none;
  letter-spacing: 0;
}

.fz-why-us__feature p {
  color: #6b6b8a;
  font-size: 0.84rem;
  line-height: 1.55;
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 989px) {
  .fz-why-us__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Why Choose Us",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Why Choose Us"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
